{"consensus_set_id":"36234","translation_language":"fa","translation_source":{"hid":"402457"},"segments":[{"source_hadith_segment":"« قَالَ اَللَّهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ :   <quranic_text> « وَ قٰالَتِ الْيَهُودُ لَيْسَتِ النَّصٰاريٰ عَليٰ شَيْءٍ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ البقرة ۱۱۳ ] </footnote>  مِنَ الدِّينِ ،  بَلْ دِينُهُمْ بَاطِلٌ وَ كُفْرٌ <quranic_text> « وَ قٰالَتِ النَّصٰاريٰ لَيْسَتِ الْيَهُودُ عَليٰ شَيْءٍ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ البقرة ۱۱۳ ] </footnote>  مِنَ الدِّينِ ،  بَلْ دِينُهُمْ بَاطِلٌ وَ كُفْرٌ <quranic_text> « وَ هُمْ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ البقرة ۱۱۳ ] </footnote>  الْيَهُودُ  <quranic_text> « يَتْلُونَ الْكِتٰابَ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ البقرة ۱۱۳ ] </footnote>  التَّوْرَاةَ »","translation_segment":"","segment_columns":[{"kind":"word","token":"قال","display":"قَالَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الله","display":"اَللَّهُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"عز","display":"عَزَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"جل","display":"جَلَّ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قالت","display":"قٰالَتِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"اليهود","display":"الْيَهُودُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ليست","display":"لَيْسَتِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"النصاري","display":"النَّصٰاريٰ"},{"kind":"word","token":"علي","display":"عَليٰ"},{"kind":"word","token":"شيء","display":"شَيْءٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قالت","display":"قٰالَتِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"النصاري","display":"النَّصٰاريٰ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ليست","display":"لَيْسَتِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"اليهود","display":"الْيَهُودُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"علي","display":"عَليٰ"},{"kind":"word","token":"شيء","display":"شَيْءٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"هم","display":"هُمْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"يتلون","display":"يَتْلُونَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الكتاب","display":"الْكِتٰابَ"},{"kind":"word","tok